<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SESSION: The Forest of Lost Instincts -->
<!-- Duration: 25 minutes | Style: Spiritual/Archetypal -->
<!-- Archetypes: The Hunter, The Trickster, The Wise Animal -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SECTION: PRE-TALK -->
<!-- Duration: 3 minutes | Pitch: 0st | Purpose: Ground and prepare -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="0st">

Welcome. <break time="1s"/>

I invite you to settle into a comfortable position now, <break time="700ms"/>
knowing that what you're about to experience <break time="500ms"/>
is a journey into a very special place. <break time="1s"/>

Within each of us lives an ancient forest. <break time="1.2s"/>
A place where our deepest instincts dwell, <break time="700ms"/>
waiting to share their wisdom with us. <break time="1.5s"/>

For too long, perhaps, <break time="500ms"/>
civilization has asked us to ignore these primal voices. <break time="1s"/>
To suppress the wild knowing that lives in our bodies. <break time="1.2s"/>
To pretend we are only thinking beings, <break time="700ms"/>
cut off from the ancient intelligence <break time="500ms"/>
that guided our ancestors through countless generations. <break time="2s"/>

Today, you will walk into that forest. <break time="1s"/>
And there, <break time="500ms"/>
you will meet three guides <break time="700ms"/>
who carry different aspects of your instinctual wisdom. <break time="1.5s"/>

The Hunter, <break time="700ms"/> who knows the power of patience and precision. <break time="1s"/>
The Trickster, <break time="700ms"/> who remembers how to play and transform. <break time="1s"/>
And the Wise Animal, <break time="700ms"/> who holds the body's deepest knowing. <break time="2s"/>

Know that throughout this journey, <break time="700ms"/>
you remain completely safe. <break time="1s"/>
You can return to ordinary awareness at any moment <break time="500ms"/>
simply by opening your eyes. <break time="1.2s"/>
But if you choose to continue, <break time="700ms"/>
trust that your instincts will guide you <break time="500ms"/>
exactly where you need to go. <break time="2s"/>

So let us begin. <break time="1.5s"/>

</prosody>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SECTION: INDUCTION -->
<!-- Duration: 4 minutes | Pitch: -2st | Purpose: Progressive relaxation -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="-2st">

Allow your eyes to close now, <break time="1s"/>
if they haven't already. <break time="1.5s"/>

And simply notice your breathing. <break time="1.2s"/>
Not changing it. <break time="700ms"/>
Just noticing. <break time="2s"/>

Notice how each breath in <break time="700ms"/>
brings fresh energy into your body. <break time="1.2s"/>
And each breath out <break time="700ms"/>
carries away anything you no longer need. <break time="2s"/>

With each breath now, <break time="1s"/>
allow your body to grow heavier. <break time="1.2s"/>
More relaxed. <break time="1.5s"/>
More connected to the surface beneath you. <break time="2s"/>

Feel that heaviness beginning in your feet. <break time="1.2s"/>
Your feet becoming so pleasantly heavy. <break time="1s"/>
As if roots are beginning to grow from them, <break time="700ms"/>
reaching down into the earth below. <break time="2s"/>

That heaviness spreading now <break time="700ms"/>
up through your ankles. <break time="1s"/>
Into your calves. <break time="1.2s"/>
Rising through your knees <break time="700ms"/>
and into your thighs. <break time="1.5s"/>

Your legs becoming so wonderfully relaxed, <break time="1s"/>
so pleasantly weighted, <break time="700ms"/>
as those roots grow deeper still. <break time="2s"/>

And now that relaxation flowing into your hips, <break time="1s"/>
your lower back, <break time="700ms"/>
softening. <break time="500ms"/>
Releasing. <break time="1.5s"/>

Up through your belly, <break time="700ms"/>
which rises and falls so gently with each breath. <break time="1.2s"/>
Through your chest, <break time="700ms"/>
your shoulders dropping now, <break time="1s"/>
any tension simply melting away. <break time="2s"/>

Down through your arms, <break time="700ms"/>
your hands, <break time="500ms"/>
your fingertips. <break time="1.2s"/>
Everything softening. <break time="1.5s"/>

And finally up through your neck, <break time="1s"/>
your jaw releasing, <break time="700ms"/>
your face smoothing, <break time="700ms"/>
even the tiny muscles around your eyes <break time="500ms"/>
letting go completely now. <break time="2s"/>

Good. <break time="1.5s"/>

You are standing now <break time="700ms"/>
at the edge of an ancient forest. <break time="1.2s"/>
Twilight is deepening around you. <break time="1s"/>
The last light of day <break time="500ms"/>
painting the sky in shades of amber and violet. <break time="1.5s"/>

Before you, <break time="700ms"/>
the forest waits. <break time="1s"/>
Ancient trees rising into the gathering darkness. <break time="1.2s"/>
Mist beginning to curl between their trunks. <break time="1.5s"/>
And somewhere deep within, <break time="700ms"/>
you feel a pull. <break time="1s"/>
Something calling you home. <break time="2s"/>

</prosody>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
