<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SECTION: JOURNEY - THE HUNTER -->
<!-- Duration: 3 minutes | Pitch: -1st | Purpose: First archetypal encounter -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->


<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="-1st">

A sound echoes through the trees. <break time="1.5s"/>
A wolf's howl. <break time="1s"/>
Distant but clear. <break time="1.2s"/>
And you know <break time="500ms"/>
