<emphasis level="moderate">Trust your timing.</emphasis> <break time="1.2s"/>
<emphasis level="moderate">Your instincts know when to move</emphasis> <break time="700ms"/>
<emphasis level="moderate">before your mind does.</emphasis> <break time="2s"/>

Feel that gift settling into your body now. <break time="1.2s"/>
That coiled, patient energy <break time="700ms"/>
in your solar plexus. <break time="1.5s"/>
This is the Hunter's gift to you. <break time="1.2s"/>
Available whenever you need it. <break time="2s"/>

The Wolf bows its head once, <break time="1s"/>
then turns and disappears into the shadows, <break time="1.2s"/>
leaving you with its gift. <break time="2.5s"/>

</prosody>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SECTION: JOURNEY - THE TRICKSTER -->
<!-- Duration: 3 minutes | Pitch: -1st | Purpose: Second archetypal encounter -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="-1st">

A different sound reaches you now. <break time="1.2s"/>
