The Trickster. <break time="1.5s"/>

Its red-gold fur seems almost to glow. <break time="1.2s"/>
Its eyes hold a spark of mischief, <break time="700ms"/>
of barely contained delight. <break time="1.5s"/>
It looks at you <break time="500ms"/>
as if it knows a wonderful secret <break time="700ms"/>
