As you approach, <break time="1s"/>
something shifts in your chest. <break time="1.2s"/>
A bubbling sensation. <break time="700ms"/>
Like champagne. <break time="500ms"/>
Like contained laughter wanting to spill out. <break time="1.5s"/>
The feeling of play <break time="500ms"/>
