leaving you with its gift. <break time="2.5s"/>

</prosody>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SECTION: JOURNEY - THE WISE ANIMAL -->
<!-- Duration: 4 minutes | Pitch: -1st | Purpose: Third archetypal encounter -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="-1st">

The forest grows older around you now. <break time="1.2s"/>
